 -------------------------------------
| *CONTROLS*                          |
| To use a floating number, press '.' |
| TO ERASE PRESS 'x'                  |
| TO QUIT THE PROGRAM PRESS 'q'       |
 -------------------------------------

 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
| *INSTALL*																				    |
| To install type "sudo cp math-crusher /usr/local/bin".  				    |
| Then to launch it, just type "math-crusher" on your terminal emulator. |
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
